Nigerian celebrities, Banky and Adesuwa Wellington have welcomed a baby boy. The couple announced the arrival of their son on their Instagram pages. Adesuwa in celebration of her birthday alongside a picture of her with a baby bump said she gave birth four weeks ago. Her post read: “You have a track record of keeping your word. “Four weeks ago, I received the best birthday gift. Our son.” Similarly, Banky W on his page while celebrating his wife revealed their son’s name as ‘Zaiah’ His post read: “Nothing I can say or do can top what God gave us. “My baby had a baby and he’s everything we prayed for. Happy Birthday “Mama Zaiah “ Recall that Banky W and Adesuwa had their white wedding in November 2017 in South Africa which had many celebrities in attendance.  